  <sys:String x:Key="UI_Epg_MatchRules_Title">Matching Rules &amp; Placeholders</sys:String>
  <sys:String x:Key="UI_Epg_MatchRules_Desc">Order: 1) Exact tvg-id match; 2) Exact name match to EPG display-name; 3) Cleaned-name equality (remove tags like HD/HEVC, unify digits); 4) Smart fuzzy match (CCTV numbers must be identical; satellite TV suffixes treated as aliases). When enabled, smart matches are cached for speed.</sys:String>
